caption: This spot simply knows how to take care of their customers. Consistently with a welcoming demeanor. The food is fairly priced, constantly flavorful and clean.

Spumante has been our "go to" restaurant for at least 25 years, from back when it was on Ventura Boulevard.  We celebrate holidays, birthdays, graduations - you name the occasion and we're at Spumante's celebrating it. And all the evenings in between.
